    {"id":"trace_t","type":"text","x":65,"y":1113,"width":2270,"height":274,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#78350f","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":81,"version":1,"versionNonce":81,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746500000000,"index":"bK","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"TRACEABILITY CHAIN — trace Task 4-5 backward:\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nTask 4-5  'KDS item status cycle: PATCH item + recalculateTotalAmount + WS broadcast'\n    ↑ came from\nSpec_4 §5.2  PATCH /api/v1/orders/:id/items/:itemId/status · Chef+\n             side effects: recalculateTotalAmount() · WS /ws/kitchen · WS /ws/orders-live\n    ↑ came from\nSRS §4.3  'Chef cập nhật trạng thái từng món → trigger recalculate total amount'\n          'BR-004: recalculateTotalAmount() after every order_items mutation'\n    ↑ came from\nBRD §1.2  'KDS: cập nhật trạng thái từng món' — listed under Phase 1 scope\n\nIF THE CHAIN BREAKS:\n  Cannot find task in spec  → you are guessing the implementation contract\n  Cannot find spec in SRS   → you are guessing the business rule\n  Cannot find SRS in BRD    → you are building something nobody agreed on → 🔴 STOP","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"TRACEABILITY CHAIN — trace Task 4-5 backward:\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nTask 4-5  'KDS item status cycle: PATCH item + recalculateTotalAmount + WS broadcast'\n    ↑ came from\nSpec_4 §5.2  PATCH /api/v1/orders/:id/items/:itemId/status · Chef+\n             side effects: recalculateTotalAmount() · WS /ws/kitchen · WS /ws/orders-live\n    ↑ came from\nSRS §4.3  'Chef cập nhật trạng thái từng món → trigger recalculate total amount'\n          'BR-004: recalculateTotalAmount() after every order_items mutation'\n    ↑ came from\nBRD §1.2  'KDS: cập nhật trạng thái từng món' — listed under Phase 1 scope\n\nIF THE CHAIN BREAKS:\n  Cannot find task in spec  → you are guessing the implementation contract\n  Cannot find spec in SRS   → you are guessing the business rule\n  Cannot find SRS in BRD    → you are building something nobody agreed on → 🔴 STOP","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false},

