    {"id":"fail_t","type":"text","x":2415,"y":1113,"width":2280,"height":274,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#7f1d1d","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":83,"version":1,"versionNonce":83,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746500000000,"index":"bM","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"FAILURE MODES — What breaks when a level is skipped:\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nSkip BRD scope check\n  → Dev builds Phase 2 feature (inventory, reports) during Phase 1 sprint → wasted sprint\n\nSkip SRS business rules\n  → Spec has no cancel validation → dev doesn't implement 30% check → customers cancel served orders\n  → Spec has no HMAC rule → dev doesn't verify webhook → payment replay attack possible\n\nSkip Spec field names (use DB_SCHEMA directly from memory)\n  → Uses base_price instead of price → sqlc compile error · or worse: silent wrong value\n  → Uses staff_id instead of created_by → wrong field stored in DB\n\nSkip FE Step 0 wireframe\n  → Discovers [PrepPanel] needs to exist mid-coding 3 other components → redesign mid-sprint\n  → Page layout wrong because zones were never drawn → full rewrite of page.tsx\n\nTask with no spec_ref (FE)\n  → No traceability → can't verify 'done' → AC unknown → built the wrong component","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"FAILURE MODES — What breaks when a level is skipped:\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nSkip BRD scope check\n  → Dev builds Phase 2 feature (inventory, reports) during Phase 1 sprint → wasted sprint\n\nSkip SRS business rules\n  → Spec has no cancel validation → dev doesn't implement 30% check → customers cancel served orders\n  → Spec has no HMAC rule → dev doesn't verify webhook → payment replay attack possible\n\nSkip Spec field names (use DB_SCHEMA directly from memory)\n  → Uses base_price instead of price → sqlc compile error · or worse: silent wrong value\n  → Uses staff_id instead of created_by → wrong field stored in DB\n\nSkip FE Step 0 wireframe\n  → Discovers [PrepPanel] needs to exist mid-coding 3 other components → redesign mid-sprint\n  → Page layout wrong because zones were never drawn → full rewrite of page.tsx\n\nTask with no spec_ref (FE)\n  → No traceability → can't verify 'done' → AC unknown → built the wrong component","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false},

    {"id":"key_r","type":"rectangle","x":50,"y":1403,"width":4660,"height":200,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#334155","backgroundColor":"#f1f5f9","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":{"type":3},"seed":90,"version":1,"versionNonce":90,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746500000000,"index":"bN","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null},
    {"id":"key_t","type":"text","x":65,"y":1411,"width":4630,"height":184,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e293b","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":91,"version":1,"versionNonce":91,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746500000000,"index":"bO","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"KEY PRINCIPLES SUMMARY\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n1. ONE FACT, ONE HOME  ·  Field names → DB_SCHEMA_SUMMARY only  ·  Error codes → ERROR_CONTRACT only  ·  Endpoint shapes → API_CONTRACT only  ·  Business rules → MASTER §4 only\n2. SCOPE GATE  ·  Do not write spec or task for anything not in BRD Phase 1. Period.\n3. RULE GATE   ·  Do not write a spec section without numbered business rules + AC from SRS. A spec with no validation rules = developer will guess.\n4. CONTRACT GATE  ·  A spec section is complete only when a developer can implement it with zero guessing. Missing field type → ❓ CLARIFY. Do not proceed.\n5. BOUNDARY RULE  ·  Split tasks by: different business rule · different protocol · mandatory side effect (BE) · different component (FE). Do NOT split by line count.\n6. FE WIREFRAME IS NOT OPTIONAL  ·  Wireframe → decompose → task rows WITH spec_ref + draw_ref → THEN code. Skipping wireframe = discovering layout problems mid-code.","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"KEY PRINCIPLES SUMMARY\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n1. ONE FACT, ONE HOME  ·  Field names → DB_SCHEMA_SUMMARY only  ·  Error codes → ERROR_CONTRACT only  ·  Endpoint shapes → API_CONTRACT only  ·  Business rules → MASTER §4 only\n2. SCOPE GATE  ·  Do not write spec or task for anything not in BRD Phase 1. Period.\n3. RULE GATE   ·  Do not write a spec section without numbered business rules + AC from SRS. A spec with no validation rules = developer will guess.\n4. CONTRACT GATE  ·  A spec section is complete only when a developer can implement it with zero guessing. Missing field type → ❓ CLARIFY. Do not proceed.\n5. BOUNDARY RULE  ·  Split tasks by: different business rule · different protocol · mandatory side effect (BE) · different component (FE). Do NOT split by line count.\n6. FE WIREFRAME IS NOT OPTIONAL  ·  Wireframe → decompose → task rows WITH spec_ref + draw_ref → THEN code. Skipping wireframe = discovering layout problems mid-code.","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false}

